description:
At the end of this course, you will get the knowledge of...

Overview of Workflow, Overview of Oracle Workflow Builder, Item types, Attribute types and Lookup Type, Messages and Activities, Getting started with Process Diagram.

Learn about Roles, Standard Activities, Predefined Workflow Activities, Concurrent Manager Standard Activities, Defining Procedures and Functions.

Business Event System, Agents and Event Subscriptions, Predefined Events, The Workflow Send Protocol, Error Handling in Oracle workflow.
title: Oracle Workflow
